lead_paragraph: Dez Bryant could be joining Tony Romo on the sidelines again, just like a year ago when Dallas slid from first place to last in the NFC East without the two offensive stars.

headline.print_headline: Cowboys' Bryant Has Hairline Knee Fracture, Outlook Unclear
